<br>
He is suprisingly easy to hold aggro on...<br>
<br>
Don't put your healers near corners and if people do get stuck have them turn round face the wall and duck then walk backward<br>
<br>
If people get put on the ice slope then have them face back down and jump to make em go down instead of up...<br>
<br>
